ndle dynamic retrieval as expected.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring object reading**\\n\\nI'm reflecting on how the `readObject` method reads a `BCLMSPublicKey` object, which leads to dynamic reflection and resolves to a byte array. This helps clarify my understanding of `BCLMSPrivateKeyTest`. It seems like I need to create a similar solution for `BCLMSPublicKey`, but simply using a byte array for read and write won’t be sufficient. So I’ll need a more complex approach. This is an interesting challenge to tackle!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering Native metadata for BCLMSPublicKey**\\n\\nI think I need to look into the fact that the Native might still be missing metadata for the BCLMSPublicKey object's newInstance before readObject. However, it seems that with the metadata generated from the agent, it should be fine. The dynamic coverage from JVM is seeing nested library serialization, so I should probably focus on editing this to custom streams. It's a bit technical, but let’s get it right!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_JCD6sQ4KAv3qNCofsrfTcdW7|fc_05c22eae10e6d90e016a263706e43c8195b00d9b163762d7b8", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/BCLMSPublicKeyTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\nimport java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\nimport java.io.ObjectInputStream;\nimport java.io.ObjectOutputStream;\n\nimport org.bouncycastle.pqc.crypto.lms.LMOtsParameters;", "newText": "import java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\nimport java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\nimport java.io.IOException;\nimport java.io.ObjectInputStream;\nimport java.io.ObjectOutputStream;\n\nimport org.bouncycastle.asn1.x509.SubjectPublicKeyInfo;\nimport org.bouncycastle.pqc.crypto.lms.LMOtsParameters;"}, {"oldText": "    private static byte[] serialize(BCLMSPublicKey publicKey) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream byteOutputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (ObjectOutputStream objectOutputStream = new ObjectOutputStream(byteOutputStream)) {\n            objectOutputStream.writeObject(publicKey);\n        }\n        return byteOutputStream.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static BCLMSPublicKey deserialize(byte[] serialized) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream objectInputStream = new ObjectInputStream(\n                new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized))) {\n            return (BCLMSPublicKey)objectInputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n", "newText": "    private static byte[] serialize(BCLMSPublicKey publicKey) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream byteOutputStream = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (ObjectOutputStream objectOutputStream = new EncodedPublicKeyReplacingObjectOutputStream(\n                byteOutputStream)) {\n            objectOutputStream.writeObject(publicKey);\n        }\n        return byteOutputStream.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static BCLMSPublicKey deserialize(byte[] serialized) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream objectInputStream = new EncodedPublicKeyResolvingObjectInputStream(\n                new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized))) {\n            return (BCLMSPublicKey)objectInputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class EncodedPublicKeyReplacingObjectOutputStream extends ObjectOutputStream {\n        private boolean replacedEncodedKey;\n\n        private EncodedPublicKeyReplacingObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream)\n                throws IOException {\n            super(outputStream);\n            enableReplaceObject(true);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Object replaceObject(Object object) throws IOException {\n            if (!replacedEncodedKey && object instanceof byte[]) {\n                replacedEncodedKey = true;\n                return new BCLMSPublicKey(SubjectPublicKeyInfo.getInstance((byte[])object));\n            }\n            return super.replaceObject(object);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class EncodedPublicKeyResolvingObjectInputStream extends ObjectInputStream {\n        private boolean resolvedNestedKey;\n\n        private EncodedPublicKeyResolvingObjectInputStream(ByteArrayInputStream inputStream)\n                throws IOException {\n            super(inputStream);\n            enableResolveObject(true);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Object resolveObject(Object object) throws IOException {\n            if (!resolvedNestedKey && object instanceof BCLMSPublicKey) {\n                resolvedNestedKey = true;\n                return ((BCLMSPublicKey)object).getEncoded();\n            }\n            return super.resolveObject(object);\n        }\n    }\n"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2133, "output": 2161, "cacheRead": 43520, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 47814, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780889311337, "responseId": "resp_05c22eae10e6d90e016a2636e011c48195b6882cecff40f1eb"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_JCD6sQ4KAv3qNCofsrfTcdW7|fc_05c22eae10e6d90e016a263706e43c8195b00d9b163762d7b8", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully replaced 2 block(s) in tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/BCLMSPublicKeyTest.java."}], "details": {"diff": "     ...\n  10 import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;\n  11 \n  12 import java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\n  13 import java.io.ByteArrayOutputStream;\n+ 14 import java.io.IOException;\n  14 import java.io.ObjectInputStream;\n  15 import java.io.ObjectOutputStream;\n  16 \n+ 18 import org.bouncycastle.asn1.x509.SubjectPublicKeyInfo;\n  17 import org.bouncycastle.pqc.crypto.lms.LMOtsPa